<div><head>晉春秋</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1238_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1238_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1238_CHANT_001-1a.2">大興中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1238_CHANT_001-1a.3">衡陽區純作鼠市，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1238_CHANT_001-1a.4">四方丈餘開門，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1238_CHANT_001-1a.5">門有一木人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1238_CHANT_001-1a.6">縱四五鼠于中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1238_CHANT_001-1a.7">欲出門，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1238_CHANT_001-1a.8">木人輒以椎椎之。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1238_CHANT_001-1a.9">吳有張衡，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1238_CHANT_001-1a.10">字思真，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1238_CHANT_001-1a.11">明達天官，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1238_CHANT_001-1a.12">能為機巧。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1238_CHANT_001-1a.13">作渾天儀，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1238_CHANT_001-1a.14">使地居中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1238_CHANT_001-1a.15">以機動之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1238_CHANT_001-1a.16">若天轉而地止，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1238_CHANT_001-1a.17">以上應度。<lb/></seg>
</p>
